thread.title: "Marvel's Jessica Jones" trailer

author: VERNE GAY
title: "Marvel's Jessica Jones" trailer
text:
"Marvel's Jessica Jones," one of the more eagerly anticipated Marvel series coming from Netflix, has finally released its official trailer.
Arriving Nov. 20, here's what else you need to know, gratis Netflix:
"After a tragic ending to her short-lived Super Hero stint, Jessica Jones is rebuilding her personal life and career as a detective who gets pulled into cases in New York City. Krysten Ritter (Jessica Jones) is joined by an amazing cast including David Tennant (Kilgrave), Mike Colter (Luke Cage), Rachael Taylor (Trish Walker), Carrie-Anne Moss, Eka Darville, Erin Moriarty, and Wil Traval, among others."
